# MOD-CSS: Covenant Design System

- **Write:** app/style.css ONLY
- **Read:** All app/*.html files
- **Focus:** UI-UX.md, DEVELOPMENT.md
- **Key Constraints:** C-04, C-05, C-11, C-12, C-13, C-14

Single CSS file with token system. Dark mode only (C-13).
- All colors via CSS custom properties in :root (C-11)
- No CSS nesting, @layer, @container (C-04 — NMCI baseline)
- Typography: Verdana (display, body), DM Mono (data) (C-12)
- PRD colors are semantically locked to urgency tiers (C-14)
Do NOT modify any app/*.html files or app/app.js from this module.
